title: The Cut 001 [December 4th 2013]
description:

    =============

====================================

 The music you want how you want it

====================================

I sort through thousands of new songs from all over the internet each month and compile the best of the best and up till now I havent uploaded them.

This is a 40 song comalation of Original/Album Mixes of a large variaty of of EDM and Rap released in the fall of 2013.

Included genres:

 - Trap
 - Rap
 - Elecro House
 - Progressive House
 - Techno
 - Trance
 - Moombahton
 - Deep House
 - Dubstep
 - Downtempo

All songs are high quality in MP3 320Kbps format. 
All songs are fully tagged with the right song art.
